public class Example {
    public void foo(int i) {
        switch (i) {
            case 1:
                // Corrected: Add a condition that breaks out of the loop
                if (true) {
                    break;
                }
                System.out.println("This will not be printed");
                break;
            default:
                System.out.println("Default case");
        }
    }
}
```

