- **Case "NorwegianBlueParrot"`: For Norwegian Blue Parrots, another conditional check is performed. If the voltage (`voltage`) exceeds 100, the method returns "scorched"; otherwise, it returns "beautiful".

- **Default Case**: If none of the above cases match, the method returns "unknown".

